WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.595
In Spain we feel very, 

00:00:01.595 --> 00:00:02.358
very, very,

00:00:02.401 --> 00:00:06.489
very proud of our public health system.

00:00:06.521 --> 00:00:07.255
In Madrid

00:00:07.256 --> 00:00:12.211
7,291 people died without medical assistance

00:00:12.212 --> 00:00:13.716
between March and April,

00:00:13.717 --> 00:00:14.939
of 2,020.

00:00:15.360 --> 00:00:18.231
There was 1 protocol approved by the Community of Madrid

00:00:18.232 --> 00:00:20.697
with Isabel DÃ­az Ayuso at the head,

00:00:21.006 --> 00:00:24.273
