00:00:24.406 --> 00:00:25.636
to hospitals.

00:00:25.726 --> 00:00:27.005
The Madrid Prosecutor's Office

00:00:27.086 --> 00:00:30.416
did not investigate the deaths in the residences.

00:00:31.398 --> 00:00:33.930
Political commissions of inquiry

00:00:33.931 --> 00:00:35.871
