00:00:38.798 --> 00:00:42.404
Ayuso has not received any of the 3 associations

00:00:42.405 --> 00:00:44.202
of victims in Madrid.

00:00:44.640 --> 00:00:48.150
It is a policy of silence in the face of 1 tragedy

00:00:48.151 --> 00:00:51.740
