00:00:51.741 --> 00:00:53.270
It is unbearable

00:00:53.271 --> 00:00:54.740
political leaders

00:00:54.741 --> 00:00:56.120
to let people die

00:00:56.121 --> 00:00:58.792
and that this has no consequences
